{"id": "art-5051", "label": "Art. 5051", "title": "Art. 5051: Informarea suspectului sau inculpatului minor", "slug": "art-5051", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2039220590\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1239\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2039220590\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 505<sup>1</sup>:\nInformarea suspectului sau inculpatului minor </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1639174644\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1238\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1639174644\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cauzele cu\nsuspec&#355;i sau inculpa&#355;i minori, înainte de prima audiere, acestora li\nse aduc la cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;, pe lâng&#259; cele prev&#259;zute la art.\n108, &#351;i urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_850428513\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1237\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_850428513\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)informa&#355;ii cu privire la principalele etape ale\nprocesului penal;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1542332871\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1236\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1542332871\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)dreptul ca p&#259;rin&#355;ii sau, dup&#259; caz,\ntutorele, curatorul ori persoana în îngrijirea sau supravegherea c&#259;reia se\nafl&#259; temporar minorul sau un alt adult care este desemnat de minor &#351;i\nacceptat în aceast&#259; calitate de organul judiciar s&#259; primeasc&#259;\nacelea&#351;i informa&#355;ii comunicate minorului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_95125169\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1235\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_95125169\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)dreptul la protec&#355;ia vie&#355;ii private, în\ncondi&#355;iile legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_605847545\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1234\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_605847545\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)dreptul de a fi înso&#355;i&#355;i de p&#259;rin&#355;i\nsau, dup&#259; caz, tutore, curator ori persoana în îngrijirea sau\nsupravegherea c&#259;reia se afl&#259; temporar minorul sau de un alt adult care\neste desemnat de minor &#351;i acceptat în aceast&#259; calitate de organul\njudiciar, în timpul diferitelor etape ale procedurii conform prezentei legi;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_591205528\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1233\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_591205528\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)dreptul de a fi evalua&#355;i prin intermediul\nreferatului de evaluare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1164737664\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1232\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1164737664\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)dreptul la evaluare medical&#259; &#351;i\nasisten&#355;&#259; medical&#259; în cazul în care vor fi supu&#351;i unei\nm&#259;suri preventive privative de libertate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_395205674\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1231\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_395205674\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)m&#259;surile preventive ce li se pot aplica, precum\n&#351;i dreptul ca m&#259;sura preventiv&#259; privativ&#259; de libertate\ns&#259; fie aplicat&#259; cu caracter excep&#355;ional, potrivit art. 243,\nperioada pentru care poate fi dispus&#259; &#351;i durata maxim&#259; a\nm&#259;surii preventive privative de libertate, condi&#355;iile pentru\nprelungirea &#351;i men&#355;inerea acesteia, precum &#351;i dreptul la\nverificarea periodic&#259; a m&#259;surii, în condi&#355;iile legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_54617762\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1230\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_54617762\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)dreptul de a fi prezen&#355;i la judecarea cauzei;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1841981698\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1229\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1841981698\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)dreptul la exercitarea c&#259;ilor de atac, în\ncondi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_487230041\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1228\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_487230041\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Toate comunic&#259;rile c&#259;tre suspectul sau\ninculpatul minor se fac într-un limbaj simplu &#351;i accesibil, adaptat\nvârstei acestuia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_958573381\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1227\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_958573381\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Informa&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 108, precum\n&#351;i cele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) se comunic&#259; &#351;i\np&#259;rin&#355;ilor sau, dup&#259; caz, tutorelui, curatorului ori persoanei\nîn îngrijirea sau supravegherea c&#259;reia se afl&#259; temporar minorul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_497966549\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1226\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_497966549\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care persoanele prev&#259;zute la alin. (3)\nnu au putut fi g&#259;site sau comunicarea c&#259;tre acestea ar fi\ncontrar&#259; interesului superior al minorului sau ar afecta\ndesf&#259;&#351;urarea procesului penal, comunicarea informa&#355;iilor\nprev&#259;zute la art. 108, precum &#351;i a celor prev&#259;zute la alin. (1)\nse face c&#259;tre un alt adult desemnat de minor &#351;i acceptat de organul\njudiciar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1994930322\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1225\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1994930322\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul în care minorul nu desemneaz&#259; un alt adult\nconform alin. (4) sau adultul desemnat nu este acceptat de organul judiciar,\ncomunicarea informa&#355;iilor se va face c&#259;tre o alt&#259; persoan&#259;\naleas&#259; de organul judiciar, &#355;inând seama de interesul superior al\nminorului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1187659437\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1224\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1187659437\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În cazul în care circumstan&#355;ele prev&#259;zute la\nalin. (4) înceteaz&#259;, comunicarea se va face c&#259;tre p&#259;rin&#355;i,\ntutore, curator ori persoana în îngrijirea sau supravegherea c&#259;reia se\nafl&#259; temporar minorul.</span></p>"}